{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["A Glorious Interlude\n\n<size=45>Chapter 4 - The Queen Incident Pt. 2<\/size>",1]]},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"As for how I intend to prove Ark Royal's innocence, my case stands on three legs——","dir":1,"bgm":"story-1","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_school","actor":207060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"First: Ark Royal originally intended to join our aircraft carrier exercises, and found herself sharing the path with the recently returned commission team, making it trivial for her to escort them.","actor":207060,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_school","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Second: Had Ark Royal truly intended to tail Lady Warspite, there is no way the Grand Old Lady would not have been able to perceive her actions.","actor":207060,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_school","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Lastly we have the question of motive... I firmly believe Ark Royal is a straightforward and upright individual, without a wicked bone in her body!","actor":207060,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_school","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Huh.","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"action":[{"type":"shake","y":7.5,"delay":0,"dur":0.1,"number":1,"X":0}],"bgName":"bg_story_school","actor":205020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Huh.","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"action":[{"type":"shake","y":7.5,"delay":0,"dur":0.1,"number":1,"X":0}],"bgName":"bg_story_school","actor":205010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Huh.","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"action":[{"type":"shake","y":7.5,"delay":0,"dur":0.1,"number":1,"X":0}],"bgName":"bg_story_school","actor":202120},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Huuh?!","actor":205020,"subActors":[{"actor":205010,"pos":{"x":555}},{"actor":202120,"pos":{"x":1125}}],"actorName":"Together","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dialogShake":{"x":8.5,"number":3,"speed":0.1},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_school","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Glorious... You...","actor":207020,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_school","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"I know what it's like to have little ones you care about, like little sisters to— No, they're even more important to me than a little sister.","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_school","actor":207060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"So I fully understand Ark Royal's impulse to cherish and protect the destroyers as one would a precious flower!","actor":207060,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_school","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"“Complete the Mission and Leave No Man Behind”— Such is the duty of the battle fleet, and our core virtue in the Royal Navy!","actor":207060,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_school","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"No doubt Ark Royal also keeps to these lofty ideals, and in this case she must have strove to spare Lady Warspite's pride from harm!","actor":207060,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_school","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"......","actor":205020,"subActors":[{"actor":205010,"pos":{"x":555}},{"actor":202120,"pos":{"x":1125}}],"actorName":"Together","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_school","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Hrm, hmph! Very well! Considering the lack of evidence, I suppose I'll let you off today! Get out of my sight, Ark Royal!","actor":205010,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_school","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Bless Your Majesty's wisdom.","actor":205020,"subActors":[{"actor":202120,"pos":{"x":1125},"dir":-1}],"actorName":"Warspite＆Belfast","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_school","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Haha! I can't thank you enough, Glorious!","actor":207020,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_school","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"Think nothing of it! Only a trifle. ... It was my pleasure to see you get off, Ark Royal.","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_school","actor":207060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"It was the beginning of a beautiful friendship (?).","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_school","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"GUANGRONG4","fadeOut":1.5}